Package: claude-usage
Version: 1.1.0
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1, gir1.2-notify-0.7
Maintainer: Yupeng Chao
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: Menu bar app showing Claude API usage
 A system tray app that shows your Claude API usage at a glance.
 Includes OAuth sign-in for rate limit tracking and local Claude
 Code log parsing for token usage stats.
